  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Storekeeper (Pandan - 5 day)",
  "description": "<p>Working Hours: Mon-Fri: 9am-6pm</p><p><strong>Skills:</strong></p><ul><li>Strong knowledge of inventory control and warehouse procedures</li><li>Ability to understand and manage Bill of Materials (BOM)</li><li>Good organizational and time-management skills</li><li>Attention to detail and accuracy in stock records</li><li>Basic math and record-keeping skills</li><li>Physical stamina for lifting and moving materials</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities Include:</strong></p><ul><li>Receiving, storing, and issuing goods as per company procedures</li><li>Locate and pick items as per the BOM list</li><li>Double-check quantities and part numbers</li><li>Packed and labeled the BOM items and handed them over to the Production team</li><li>Report any missing, damaged, or substituted items</li><li>Keeping accurate records of stock levels and movements</li><li>Maintaining a clean and organized store area</li><li>Conducting regular stock checks and reporting discrepancies</li><li>To take charge of incoming and outgoing goods</li><li>To top up stock item for inhouse production / project requirement</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>This is consider as junior executive level with good insight of the overall warehouse operation</li><li>NITEC Mechanical with min 2 years working experience in store or inventory environment</li><li>Knowledge of purchasing and delivery procedure will be an added advantage</li><li>Immediate position</li></ul><p>KN TAN (R1768143) --- 41M3QWM15</p><p>JIH SUN EMPLOYMENT AGENCY(17C8778)</p>",
